<paragraph id="IFRS07_12B"><paranum>12B</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 7"/><data name="paranum" value="12B"/></prolog><body><p>An entity shall disclose if, in the current or previous reporting periods, it has reclassified any <xref base="SL37522973" href="../ias32/IAS32_11.dita#IAS32_11/IAS32_P0115">financial assets<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0123"/></ph></xref> in accordance with <xref id="IFRS07_X0262" base="F71835268" href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_g4.4.1-4.4.3.dita#IFRS09_g4.4.1-4.4.3/IFRS09_g4.4.1-4.4.3_TI">paragraph 4.4.1 of IFRS 9</xref>. For each such event, an entity shall disclose:</p><ol id="IFRS07_L0024" base="F18762601" type="lower-alpha"><li id="IFRS07_12B_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value>           <p id="IFRS07_P0211" base="F18762603">the date of reclassification.</p>         </li><li id="IFRS07_12B_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value>           <p id="IFRS07_P0212" base="F18762605">a detailed explanation of the change in business model and a qualitative description of its effect on the entity&#x2019;s financial statements.</p>         </li><li id="IFRS07_12B_c"><li_value>(c)</li_value>           <p id="IFRS07_P0213" base="F18762607">the amount reclassified into and out of each category.</p>         </li></ol></body></paragraph>